data.title: Medical City Plano Hospital
data.meta_description: Our full-service hospital is home to more than 1,800 physicians representing over 70 specialties and subspecialties, including trauma care.
data.text:
At most hospitals, you only have three hours to get treatment after a stroke. We give you 12.

What matters most to us is giving people the absolute best healthcare possible. Apply online today or register for an upcoming career event.

Fever? Headache? Cough? Sore throat? We are committed to making the right care easy to access for you and your family. Now, you can use our 24/7 online symptom checker to describe your symptoms, answer a few multiple choice questions, see your options for care, and even get home care advice. It's quick, easy and confidential.
